node.text:
Absolutely slammed at MegaCon. Great turnout and fantastic fans. 

Running around like crazy, doing drawing demo/comic panels, business meetings, and hanging out with the lovely Torpedo Comics crew during my quick meal breaks. 

One weird event: Hung out with Ryan Ottley, Ryan Kincaid, Tyler Kirkman and others in the Hyatt hot tub at 3am in the morning, after Tyler told us the hot tub was open 24 hours. Ryan Ottley is a hairy bastard. 

@frankchoartist #frankchoartist #torpedocomics #elvira #joker #megacon

node.text:
More Remarqued art prints for MegaCon. 

This show has been bonkers. My business meetings have gone well and everything is selling out. The fans been absolutely fantastic and everyone is complying with the masked mandate, which is stunning for Florida. 

I’ll be at my booth, 71P, around 11:00am. 

@frankchoartist #frankchoartist #dccomics #batman #poisonivy #harleyquinn #artprint #dance #megacon
